cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual tracking using RGBD data and proposes a deep learning-based approach for the same. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a likely category as the proposed tracker can be used for robotic applications such as object tracking and manipulation. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for tracking. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes an intelligent system for tracking objects using RGBD data. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with tracking objects in multimedia data (RGBD).
